37:18.036 --> 37:21.473
Und lift your robe.

37:32.083 --> 37:33.285
Ja.

37:49.768 --> 37:51.336
Hi. What's going on?

37:51.337 --> 37:52.737
Don't interfere.

37:52.738 --> 37:57.275
He's paying me $15,000
just to touch my behind.

37:58.810 --> 38:00.210
You! Get outta here!

38:00.211 --> 38:01.211
Please, forgive...

38:01.212 --> 38:02.681
Get out!

38:03.649 --> 38:05.950
This kind of thing
could ruin our marriage.

38:05.951 --> 38:09.387
Why? Because you
don't want me to work?

38:09.388 --> 38:12.189
Earn my own money?
Have my own career?

38:12.190 --> 38:13.924
You call this a career?

38:13.925 --> 38:17.227
Oh, I've made those veins
in your temple throb.

38:17.228 --> 38:18.864
Oh, I love that.

38:20.866 --> 38:22.800
Ha ha ha!

38:22.801 --> 38:26.771
Dolores, our marriage
lies broken on the floor

38:26.772 --> 38:29.607
like the shards of glass
on our honeymoon suite!

38:29.608 --> 38:33.678
Aah! Oh! 19th century
Indian rubber vase, eh?

38:33.679 --> 38:38.282
Dolores, I am making
a citizen's divorce.

38:38.283 --> 38:39.450
What?

38:39.451 --> 38:41.552
By the powers vested in me,

38:41.553 --> 38:46.491
I hereby declare our
marriage null and void!

38:46.492 --> 38:48.627
E Pluribus Unum!

38:52.998 --> 38:54.164
Jawohl?

38:54.165 --> 38:56.367
I'm Dr.Hfuhruhurr.

38:56.368 --> 39:00.405
Dr. hfurrrr... oh, ja.

39:00.406 --> 39:03.541
You and your wife
are expected for dinner.

39:03.542 --> 39:05.476
My wife won't be coming.

39:05.477 --> 39:06.711
Oh. I trust
she is not ill.

39:06.712 --> 39:10.314
She's not ill.
She's a cheap, vulgar slut!

39:10.315 --> 39:12.183
Ja, I've heard this.

39:14.152 --> 39:16.521
Dr. hfuhruhurr, please.

39:16.522 --> 39:20.024
No, I'm sorry, he's not in.
This is Mrs. hfurrr... Ff.

39:20.025 --> 39:22.593
I'm James Gladstone,
calling from New York.

39:22.594 --> 39:23.994
I'm the attorney

39:23.995 --> 39:26.831
for Dr. hfuhruhurr's
step-grandmother.

39:26.832 --> 39:29.299
I wanted to inform
the doctor of her passing.

39:29.300 --> 39:30.535
Passing what?

39:30.536 --> 39:33.003
She was cremated this afternoon.

39:33.004 --> 39:35.606
We need the doctor's
signature on some documents

39:35.607 --> 39:37.943
before we release
his share of the estate.

39:40.345 --> 39:42.112
Um...

39:42.113 --> 39:45.551
How big is the estate?

40:02.768 --> 40:04.770
Rebecca...

40:06.605 --> 40:09.441
Why didn't you give me a sign?

40:12.077 --> 40:14.546
I miss you.

40:16.247 --> 40:17.849
The fun we had.

40:24.389 --> 40:25.556
Remember our song?

40:25.557 --> 40:28.493
♪ If you like-a me ♪

40:28.494 --> 40:31.028
♪ Like I like-a you ♪

40:31.029 --> 40:35.766
♪ And we like-a both
the same ♪

40:35.767 --> 40:39.904
♪ I like-a say,
this very day ♪

40:39.905 --> 40:44.341
♪ I like-a change
your name ♪

40:44.342 --> 40:47.077
♪ 'Cause I love-a you ♪

40:47.078 --> 40:49.647
♪ And love-a you true ♪

40:49.648 --> 40:54.719
♪ And
if you would love-a me ♪

40:54.720 --> 40:57.522
♪ One live as two ♪

40:57.523 --> 40:59.890
♪ Two live as one ♪

40:59.891 --> 41:02.993
♪ Under the bamboo tree ♪

41:02.994 --> 41:07.998
♪ And every morning
he would be ♪

41:07.999 --> 41:12.537
♪ Down underneath
the bamboo tree ♪

41:12.538 --> 41:16.641
♪ Awaiting there
his love to see ♪

41:16.642 --> 41:20.011
♪ And to her he'd sing... ♪

41:26.251 --> 41:28.318
♪ If you like-a me ♪

41:28.319 --> 41:30.788
♪ Like I like-a you ♪

41:30.789 --> 41:34.925
♪ And we like-a
both the same ♪

41:34.926 --> 41:38.529
♪ I like-a say,
this very day.. ♪

41:38.530 --> 41:40.497
Mrs. Necessiter?

41:40.498 --> 41:43.568
♪ I like-a change
your name ♪

41:43.569 --> 41:45.570
♪ 'Cause I love-a you ♪

41:45.571 --> 41:48.438
♪ And love-a you true ♪

41:48.439 --> 41:53.177
♪ And if you love-a me ♪

41:53.178 --> 41:55.546
♪ One live as two ♪

41:55.547 --> 41:57.982
♪ Two live as one ♪

41:57.983 --> 42:01.553
♪ Under the bamboo tree ♪

42:04.923 --> 42:07.191
Hello?

42:07.192 --> 42:08.827
Hello?

42:11.062 --> 42:12.997
Is this a joke?

42:12.998 --> 42:13.998
What?

42:13.999 --> 42:15.666
Is this a joke?

42:15.667 --> 42:20.204
Who are you?
What's happening?

42:20.205 --> 42:22.607
I don't know.

42:22.608 --> 42:24.341
Who are you?

42:24.342 --> 42:26.276
Dr. Michael
hfuhruhurr.

42:26.277 --> 42:30.080
Dr. hfuhruhurr?

42:30.081 --> 42:31.481
My god.

42:31.482 --> 42:32.950
What?

42:32.951 --> 42:37.788
You're the first... Object
that ever pronounced it right.

42:37.789 --> 42:39.757
How else could you pronounce it?

42:39.758 --> 42:43.527
H-f-u-h-r-u-h-u-r-r,
isn't it?

42:43.528 --> 42:46.964
Yes!

42:46.965 --> 42:48.398
Who are you?

42:48.399 --> 42:52.637
Anne. Anne Uumellmahaye.

42:52.638 --> 42:57.708
U-u-m-e-l-l-m-a-h-a-y-e?
Uumellmahaye?

42:57.709 --> 43:01.378
Yes. Where am I?
It's so dark.

43:01.379 --> 43:03.781
In a doctor's laboratory.

43:03.782 --> 43:07.151
Am I all right?

43:07.152 --> 43:11.488
Um... Not really.

43:11.489 --> 43:15.726
Will I be able to play
the piano again?

43:15.727 --> 43:20.097
Um, I would think... no.

43:20.098 --> 43:23.500
Why did you call me an object?

43:23.501 --> 43:25.936
I'm sorry.

43:25.937 --> 43:30.574
I didn't know
what else to call you.

43:30.575 --> 43:33.210
Why?

43:33.211 --> 43:34.544
You don't know?

43:34.545 --> 43:36.546
No, I don't.

43:36.547 --> 43:38.683
Please, tell me.

43:38.684 --> 43:41.385
Well...

43:41.386 --> 43:45.956
Miss uumellmahaye, it seems
that you have no body.

43:45.957 --> 43:48.292
What happened to my body?

43:48.293 --> 43:49.960
It's dead. Gone.

43:49.961 --> 43:55.299
You're a disembodied brain
kept alive by a scientist.

43:55.300 --> 43:57.234
But we're talking.

43:57.235 --> 44:02.339
I must at least have lips,
a tongue, a throat.

44:02.340 --> 44:05.342
Nothing.
Just a jar.

44:05.343 --> 44:09.213
Oh! Oh!

44:09.214 --> 44:12.249
Don't cry.

44:12.250 --> 44:14.651
But how can I hear you?

44:14.652 --> 44:16.854
Must be some kind of telepathy.

44:16.855 --> 44:18.222
What's going to happen to me?

44:18.223 --> 44:23.193
Hans told me
you were here. Good, good.

44:23.194 --> 44:26.130
Now, let me show you

44:26.131 --> 44:29.099
that experiment
I've been working on.

44:29.100 --> 44:31.001
No! No.

44:31.002 --> 44:32.803
I've got something
more important.

44:32.804 --> 44:35.272
Listen, just listen.

44:35.273 --> 44:37.007
All right, sing.

44:37.008 --> 44:41.278
♪ If you like-a me
like I like-a you ♪

44:41.279 --> 44:45.883
♪ And we like-a both
the same ♪

44:45.884 --> 44:47.918
♪ I like-a say... ♪

44:47.919 --> 44:50.587
Have you heard anything
like that in your life?

44:50.588 --> 44:51.722
I can't hear a thing.

44:51.723 --> 44:53.623
Oh, really?

44:53.624 --> 44:54.624
Shh.

44:54.625 --> 44:55.793
What were you doing?

44:55.794 --> 44:58.896
I was just working
on my new technique

44:58.897 --> 45:00.898
for walking in corduroy pants

45:00.899 --> 45:04.668
to eliminate the scraping
when your thighs rub together.

45:04.669 --> 45:07.772
That's very
exciting work, doctor.

45:07.773 --> 45:10.674
Now, come on. Let me
show you what I've done

45:10.675 --> 45:12.710
for your friend Beckerman.

45:15.013 --> 45:17.282
Whup.
Just one moment.

45:18.750 --> 45:21.118
What happened?

45:21.119 --> 45:23.520
No one can hear you but me.

45:23.521 --> 45:26.390
Doctor!

45:26.391 --> 45:27.391
Did you hear that?

45:27.392 --> 45:28.193
No.

45:28.194 --> 45:30.895
You can't hear anyone but me.

45:30.896 --> 45:33.563
It is some kind of telepathy.

45:33.564 --> 45:34.865
I'm frightened.

45:34.866 --> 45:37.234
Don't be. Things are never
as bad as they seem.

45:37.235 --> 45:40.805
You still have your...
Brain.

45:40.806 --> 45:42.739
Dr. hfuhruhurr!

45:42.740 --> 45:44.909
I'll be back.

45:44.910 --> 45:46.945
Just stay here.

45:49.280 --> 45:52.616
I believe you know
this gentleman.

45:52.617 --> 45:55.285
Is that
Dr. Beckerman?

45:55.286 --> 45:58.588
Sort of. See,
I've devised a machine

45:58.589 --> 46:01.959
that can transfer the entire
contents of one brain

46:01.960 --> 46:03.393
into another brain.
Understand, of course,

46:03.394 --> 46:05.729
that the brain of a gorilla
is smaller than a human's,

46:05.730 --> 46:08.432
so much of Dr. Beckerman's
vast knowledge

46:08.433 --> 46:10.467
couldn't be accommodated.

46:10.468 --> 46:11.602
Dr. Beckerman?

46:15.640 --> 46:17.407
That's him all right.

46:17.408 --> 46:20.411
We never did like to
shake hands with him.

46:21.612 --> 46:23.113
He must be lonely.

46:23.114 --> 46:26.650
Perhaps soon we'll
find him a companion.

46:26.651 --> 46:28.019
Come, doctor.

46:33.424 --> 46:35.026
Bye.

46:40.966 --> 46:42.199
I'm going up to pack my clothes.

46:42.200 --> 46:43.700
Can you send the bellman
up in 10 minutes?

46:43.701 --> 46:44.903
Yes, sir.

47:15.566 --> 47:16.901
"My darling husband,

47:16.902 --> 47:20.437
"by the time you read this
I will be dead.

47:20.438 --> 47:23.007
"My only regret
is that I caused you pain.

47:23.008 --> 47:24.308
"I hope my insurance money

47:24.309 --> 47:26.276
"brings you some happiness.

47:26.277 --> 47:29.146
"May I burn in hell for
what I have done to you.

47:29.147 --> 47:30.881
"My broken body will be lying

47:30.882 --> 47:33.417
"7 floors below.

47:33.418 --> 47:34.718
"Au revoir,

47:34.719 --> 47:36.653
Dolores."

47:36.654 --> 47:38.722
Aah!

47:38.723 --> 47:40.025
No!

47:45.330 --> 47:46.363
You're alive!

47:46.364 --> 47:47.365
Yes.

47:48.566 --> 47:49.666
But the scream...

47:49.667 --> 47:50.868
I was rehearsing.

47:51.802 --> 47:53.803
Don't come near me.

47:53.804 --> 47:54.838
Why are you doing this?

47:54.839 --> 47:56.773
Because I'm evil.

47:56.774 --> 47:58.309
You're not evil.
You're sick.

47:59.477 --> 48:00.477
Sick?

48:00.478 --> 48:01.578
Yes, from the operation.

48:01.579 --> 48:03.747
Just screw your head on
a little bit tighter.

48:03.748 --> 48:05.015
You can be well.

48:05.016 --> 48:06.850
It's no use, Michael.

48:06.851 --> 48:08.718
I'm no good for you.

48:08.719 --> 48:10.587
And, besides,

48:10.588 --> 48:11.456
you divorced me.

48:11.457 --> 48:13.857
I'm making
a citizen's annulment.

48:13.858 --> 48:16.594
Ipso Facto, coitus interruptus.

48:18.063 --> 48:19.163
I'm coming to get you.

48:19.164 --> 48:21.065
No! Stay where you are.

48:21.066 --> 48:24.501
I can't stand hurting you
anymore, Michael.

48:24.502 --> 48:25.669
Good-bye, my darling.

48:25.670 --> 48:26.671
No!

48:58.836 --> 49:00.705
Take my hand.

49:04.842 --> 49:06.511
You're safe
with me now. Aah!

49:07.912 --> 49:10.515
Put your arms around my neck.

49:15.153 --> 49:19.957
I hope this is strong enough
for the both of us.

49:24.529 --> 49:25.996
Hang on.

49:25.997 --> 49:27.732
Uhh!

49:32.403 --> 49:33.404
Uhh!

49:34.272 --> 49:35.672
I don't have any more saliva.

49:35.673 --> 49:37.375
I need yours.

49:41.512 --> 49:43.147
Uhh!

49:43.148 --> 49:45.615
You're all right now.

49:45.616 --> 49:47.118
Oh!
There.

49:50.988 --> 49:52.189
You're going to the hospital.

49:52.190 --> 49:54.192
No, Michael, please.

49:54.992 --> 49:58.196
I want to make it up to you.

50:00.698 --> 50:02.099
When? Thursday?

50:02.100 --> 50:03.701
How about Monday?

50:04.969 --> 50:06.002
Next Monday?

50:06.003 --> 50:07.003
Today, Monday.

50:07.004 --> 50:08.004
Later today?

50:08.005 --> 50:09.039
Now.

50:09.040 --> 50:10.674
Right now or later now?

50:10.675 --> 50:11.841
Now now.

50:11.842 --> 50:13.711
Wow, wow.

50:37.268 --> 50:40.137
Oh, I love a clean, smooth,

50:40.138 --> 50:42.206
hairless chest.

50:42.207 --> 50:44.007
I mean hairy.

50:44.008 --> 50:45.210
Hairy.

50:55.986 --> 50:59.190
I never knew
it could be like that.

51:00.258 --> 51:02.327
Oh, it was so...

51:03.661 --> 51:04.795
So...

51:06.697 --> 51:08.433
Professional.

51:11.369 --> 51:15.573
We are finally united under
the holy laws of matrimony...

51:16.774 --> 51:18.142
In sickness

51:18.143 --> 51:19.943
and in health,

51:19.944 --> 51:21.146
till death...

51:25.850 --> 51:27.452
Do us part.

51:34.992 --> 51:36.261
Help!

51:39.464 --> 51:40.498
Help!

51:43.701 --> 51:44.802
Help!

51:48.539 --> 51:49.939
Help!

51:49.940 --> 51:51.142
Help!

52:12.230 --> 52:14.364
Dr. hfuhruhurr.

52:14.365 --> 52:15.965
Is Dr. Necessiter in?

52:15.966 --> 52:17.867
No, sir.

52:17.868 --> 52:19.102
May I wait for him?

52:19.103 --> 52:20.405
Yes.

52:29.280 --> 52:32.115
I meant, may I wait inside?

52:32.116 --> 52:33.318
Ja.

52:37.355 --> 52:39.088
May I wait in the laboratory?

52:39.089 --> 52:40.824
Oh, I'm afraid it's locked, sir,

52:40.825 --> 52:44.662
but you are welcome
to wait in the den.

52:50.100 --> 52:52.336
Make yourself comfortable, sir.

52:52.337 --> 52:54.871
Perhaps I could
bring you a drink?

52:54.872 --> 52:57.874
Yes. Uh,
Tahiti tingle.

52:57.875 --> 52:59.443
A tingle.

52:59.444 --> 53:00.744
And take your time.

53:00.745 --> 53:02.280
Ah.

53:08.486 --> 53:09.487
Damn.

53:19.930 --> 53:22.866
Aah!

53:22.867 --> 53:25.168
Are you all right, sir?

53:25.169 --> 53:26.570
I'm fine.
I'm fine.

53:26.571 --> 53:28.137
I just leaned against the door.

53:28.138 --> 53:30.808
The doors in this condo
are paper-thin.

53:33.077 --> 53:35.279
Everything today
is made so cheap.

53:35.280 --> 53:37.648
Here, look at this wall...

53:39.083 --> 53:40.584
Like paper.

53:40.585 --> 53:43.287
Here is your drink, sir.

53:43.288 --> 53:44.488
Thank you.

53:44.489 --> 53:46.456
Now can I get you
anything else, doctor?

53:46.457 --> 53:48.458
I am about to retire.

53:48.459 --> 53:49.994
Really?
You seem so young.

53:51.729 --> 53:55.064
No. I mean retire
for the night.

53:55.065 --> 53:57.166
Oh. Oh, no, thanks,
I'm fine.

53:57.167 --> 53:59.469
And don't worry about this.

53:59.470 --> 54:02.740
I'll have it replaced
in the morning.

54:05.810 --> 54:07.378
Miss uumellmahaye?

54:11.215 --> 54:12.749
Miss uumellmahaye?

54:12.750 --> 54:14.183
Dr. hfuhruhurr?

54:14.184 --> 54:15.819
Miss uumellmahaye?

54:15.820 --> 54:17.622
Dr. hfuhruhurr?

54:21.459 --> 54:22.793
Dr. hfuhruhurr.

54:25.095 --> 54:26.297
No.

54:27.197 --> 54:28.399
No.

54:31.802 --> 54:32.603
Dr. hfuhruhurr,

54:32.604 --> 54:34.905
what's happened to me?

54:36.874 --> 54:39.643
You're a gorilla.

54:39.644 --> 54:41.545
I don't feel like a gorilla.

54:41.546 --> 54:44.914
Well, you sure do look like one.

54:44.915 --> 54:46.316
But I... I can't be.

54:46.317 --> 54:49.419
I can't see or touch...

54:49.420 --> 54:51.521
Or anything.

54:51.522 --> 54:53.924
Miss uumellmahaye?

54:57.127 --> 54:58.729
Call me Anne.

54:59.864 --> 55:01.164
Thank god.

55:01.165 --> 55:02.732
You're still a brain.

55:02.733 --> 55:03.733
Oops!

55:03.734 --> 55:05.301
Hey!

55:05.302 --> 55:08.271
Why did you think
I was a gorilla?

55:08.272 --> 55:09.873
Because that's what
Dr. Necessiter

55:09.874 --> 55:11.476
has planned for you.

55:12.377 --> 55:13.877
But don't worry.

55:13.878 --> 55:15.580
I have other plans.

55:50.948 --> 55:52.816
You're in my room now.

55:52.817 --> 55:54.183
Where in your room?

55:54.184 --> 55:55.386
In a...

55:57.455 --> 55:59.456
On a gold leaf Florentine table

55:59.457 --> 56:01.391
by the window,

56:01.392 --> 56:03.460
overlooking a garden.

56:03.461 --> 56:06.831
Oh, I can almost
smell the flowers.

56:07.965 --> 56:09.734
Phew.

56:12.269 --> 56:13.336
Sleep well, Anne.

56:13.337 --> 56:16.073
Good night, Michael.

56:18.275 --> 56:19.544
Good night.

56:24.549 --> 56:25.782
Mmm.
You getting up?

56:25.783 --> 56:27.817
Yeah, yeah, just getting up.

56:27.818 --> 56:29.352
Ahh.

56:29.353 --> 56:30.654
I'll order us some breakfast.

56:30.655 --> 56:33.790
Yeah. Order me 2 sheets
of bacon and a pillow.

56:33.791 --> 56:34.792
Hmm?

56:38.596 --> 56:39.796
Hey, know what
I've been thinking?

56:39.797 --> 56:41.798
There's no need
to rush home right now.

56:41.799 --> 56:43.366
I'm due for a sabbatical,

56:43.367 --> 56:44.468
and there's a lot
of experimentation

56:44.469 --> 56:45.735
going on in this city...

56:45.736 --> 56:47.737
A lot of scientists,
a lot of brain research.

56:47.738 --> 56:49.038
You know, I could go out
and look for a cottage,

56:49.039 --> 56:50.807
and I could set up
a little laboratory.

56:50.808 --> 56:52.041
We could be very, very
comfortable there.

56:52.042 --> 56:53.677
What do you think
of an idea like that?

56:53.678 --> 56:56.312
You think I should go out
and look for one right now?

56:56.313 --> 56:57.647
Whatever you want.

56:57.648 --> 56:59.883
Do you want me to go with you?

56:59.884 --> 57:01.184
No, no, that's not
necessary, really.

57:01.185 --> 57:02.185
Oh, but I'd love to.

57:02.186 --> 57:03.319
Oh, it's so much trouble,

57:03.320 --> 57:04.320
the driving

57:04.321 --> 57:05.922
and the realtors.

57:05.923 --> 57:06.724
Yes?

57:06.724 --> 57:07.558
May I take the table?

57:07.559 --> 57:08.559
Oh, yeah, come on in.

57:08.560 --> 57:09.826
It's really...

57:09.827 --> 57:11.327
Ahem.

57:11.328 --> 57:12.395
Madame.

57:12.396 --> 57:13.564
Oh, you're right.

57:16.266 --> 57:17.300
I'd just be in the way.

57:17.301 --> 57:18.668
It's best.

57:18.669 --> 57:21.505
I think I'll just

57:21.506 --> 57:22.972
slip...

57:22.973 --> 57:25.074
Out of these clothes

57:25.075 --> 57:27.911
into a hot bath.

57:27.912 --> 57:29.145
That's great.

